file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: "Title from enunciate.xml"
  version: "version from enunciate.xml"
  description: ""
servers: []
paths:
  "/path/{pathArg}":
    put:
      description: "Summary.\n\nDescription follows..."
      tags:
        - "Resource group text"
      summary: "Summary."
      deprecated: false
      operationId: update
      parameters:
      - name: "pathArg"
        in: path
        description: "Argument on path."
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        description: ""
        required: true
        content:
          "application/json":
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/json_DataDTO"
          "application/xml":
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/xml_ns0_dataDTO"
          "text/plain":
            schema:
              type: string
              format: binary
      responses:
        "204":
          description: ""
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/json_DataDTO"
 
components:
  schemas:
    "json_DataDTO":
      title: "DataDTO"
      type: object
      properties:
        "last":
          type: string
        "first":
          type: string
      example:
        last: "..."
        first: "..."
    "xml_ns0_dataDTO":
      title: "dataDTO"
      allOf:
      - type: string
        format: binary
      - type: object
        properties:
          "first":
            type: string
          "last":
            type: string
        xml:
          name: data
          namespace: http://www.jyskebank.dk/enunciate/openapi/version/1
